  <brief_title>Changes in Quality of Life Following Surgical Treatment of Benign Non-toxic Goiter</brief_title>
  <acronym>SOLOIST</acronym>
  <official_title>The Impact of Surgical Treatment of Benign Non-toxic Goiter on Quality of Life</official_title>
