  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to investigate the influence of surgical treatment on benign non-toxic goiter on
      the disease specific quality of life evaluated 6 months after thyroid surgery.

      All investigations follow already scheduled treatments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
